wiki.content: With cheeky lyrics and catchy upbeat chorus 'If U Seek Amy' became the 24th UK hit single for Ms Spears in May 2009, just after ten years since her debut '...Baby One More Time'. Britney recently finished her UK 'Circus' tour, complete with circus theme, named after her platinum selling album of the same name.
